  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The breakfast room is decorated in a chalet style with a warming fireplace. It is a lovely atmosphere to start the day in.</p>
<p>At breakfast you'll be spoilt for choice with a huge selection of sweet and savoury choices. There's a fresh fruit bar, granola, cakes, breads, pastries and anything else you could think of. You can even get your eggs cooked to order in whatever style you please.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
