  <description><![CDATA[<p>When it comes to mountain retreats, Mountain Home Villa Anna is a beautifully designed, rustic meets modern escape. We can't get enough of the chalet style design with warm wood and alpine design throughout.</p>
<h2>Hearty breakfast</h2>
<p>As the hotel is on a bed and breakfast basis, you can fuel up for the day at the varied breakfast buffet which includes a range of regional ingredients and enjoy meals in the nearby restaurants each evening - there are plenty of restaurants a short walk away serving tasty Tyrolean specialties, pizza and pasta. </p>
<h2>Alpine retreat</h2>
<p>The charming Mountain Home Villa Anna is beautifully designed, the chalet style property has rustic wood and fireplaces throughout, as well as cosy seating areas where you can relax after a day of adventures - warm up in front of the fireplace or cosy up in front of the fire with a book in the library corner.</p>
<p>It's all about the little details, each room has a balcony overlooking the resort and surrounding mountains, plus bathrobes and slippers and bibs for the little ones. It's these touches which make this feel like a home away from home, and the staff never fail to be friendly and welcoming.</p>
<p>Access to the slopes couldn’t be more convenient! Just steps away, the Nives button lift provides a seamless start to your day on the mountain. After an exhilarating time on the slopes, you can ski back to within 100 meters of the hotel, ideal for winding down and transitioning into your après-ski plans.</p>
<h2>Unwind and relax </h2>
<p>Treat yourself to a moment of peace in the wellness area. Have a dip in the pool and soothe any aches or pains with the hydro-massage jets or unwind in the Finnish Bio Sauna.</p>
<p>There are plenty of comfortable seating areas throughout the hotel - warm up in front of the fire with a book in the library corner, and marvel at the incredible mountain views surrounding you. </p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Mountain Home Villa Anna the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
